OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs amid pressure
OL,4,Cover Mandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FThe Labour leader is expected to be
OL,7,Fgrilled at Prime Minister's Questions
OL,8,Fafter Sir Olly defended himself in
OL,9,Ffront of the Foreign Affairs Committee
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,12,FThe senior civil servant chief was
OL,13,Fsacked by the Prime Minister last week
OL,14,Fafter it emerged he did not tell him
OL,15,Fthat Lord Mandelson was cleared to
OL,16,Ftake up the top diplomatic post
OL,17,Fdespite security vetting officials
OL,18,Frecommending against it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs amid pressure
OL,4,Cover Mandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FSir Keir told the Commons on Monday he
OL,7,Fhad challenged Sir Olly over why he
OL,8,Fwent against the recommendation of UK
OL,9,FSecurity Vetting (UKSV) and did not
OL,10,Faccept his explanation.
OL,12,FBut Sir Olly said it was normal not to
OL,13,Fshare the findings of the vetting
OL,14,Fprocess and described feeling under
OL,15,Fpressure to clear the peer for the
OL,16,Frole.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs amid pressure
OL,4,Cover Mandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FWhen Sir Olly took over at the helm of
OL,7,Fthe Foreign Office in January last
OL,8,Fyear, Lord Mandelson had already gone
OL,9,Fthrough the Cabinet Office's "due
OL,10,Fdiligence" process, the King and the
OL,11,FUS had given him approval, and he was
OL,12,Falready being granted access to
OL,13,F"highly classified briefings" on a
OL,14,Fcase-by-case basis ` without his
OL,15,Fsecurity clearance being confirmed, he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@JO]uD@AOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs amid pressure
OL,4,Cover Mandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FThe Whitehall veteran said this
OL,7,Fresulted in a "dismissive approach" to
OL,8,Fdeveloped vetting from Downing Street
OL,9,Ffor the remainder of the process but
OL,10,Finsisted it was completed to the
OL,11,Fnormal standard "despite this
OL,12,Fatmosphere of pressure".
OL,14,FNo 10 has rejected this, saying there
OL,15,Fis a distinction between "the idea of
OL,16,Fpressure" and "being kept informed
OL,17,Fabout the process and the progress of
OL,18,Fthe appointment".
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@cO]sD@QOUtD@WO]wD@ZOUxD@IO]xD@
OL,26,AOOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
